    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22289722_5_3654-3796",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3654-3796",
      "markText": "浮生着甚苦奔忙，盛席华筵终散场。 悲喜千般同幻渺，古今一梦尽荒唐。 谩言红袖啼痕重，更有情痴抱恨长。 字字看来皆是血，十年辛苦不寻常！",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22289722&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3654&rangeEnd=3796",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2313294071541d3a2315836?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3654&rangeEnd=3796"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22289722_6_8266-8321",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8266-8321",
      "markText": "今之人，贫者日为衣食所累，富者又怀不足之心。总一时少闲，又有贪淫恋色，好货寻愁之事，那里去有工夫看那理治之书。",
      "totalCount": 364,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22289722&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8266&rangeEnd=8321",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2313294071541d3a2315836?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8266&rangeEnd=8321"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22289722_6_2958-2986",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2958-2986",
      "markText": "瞬息间则又乐极悲生，人非物换。究竟是到头一梦，万境归空。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22289722&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2958&rangeEnd=2986",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2313294071541d3a2315836?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2958&rangeEnd=2986"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22289722_25_13376-13437",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "13376-13437",
      "markText": "宝玉云亲不间疏，先不僣后，表面似指对钗黛关系而言，实则内含双重意义。真正之亲，真正之先皆属湘云，而黛者、钗者皆后至之人也。",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22289722&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=13376&rangeEnd=13437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2313294071541d3a2315836?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=13376&rangeEnd=13437"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22289722_73_6659-6706",
      "chapterUid": 73,
      "range": "6659-6706",
      "markText": "可见赵姨娘为人小器糊涂，饶得了东西，反说许多令人不入耳生厌的闲话，也怨不得探春生气，看不起他。",
      "totalCount": 310,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22289722&chapterUid=73&rangeStart=6659&rangeEnd=6706",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2313294071541d3a2315836?chapterUid=73&rangeStart=6659&rangeEnd=6706"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22289722_6_20343-20353",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "20343-20353",
      "markText": "今古穷酸，色心最重。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22289722&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=20343&rangeEnd=20353",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2313294071541d3a2315836?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=20343&rangeEnd=20353"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22289722_7_8336-8352",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "8336-8352",
      "markText": "身后有馀忘缩手，眼前无路想回头。",
      "totalCount": 294,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22289722&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8336&rangeEnd=8352",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2313294071541d3a2315836?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8336&rangeEnd=8352"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22289722_6_2595-2667",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2595-2667",
      "markText": "石头初心只是为向人世繁华受享快乐，是为欲望。欲是自利之私心。及其入世，经历见闻，方知俗世所缺者只是真情互待。故其终生以情反欲，此即作书之大旨也。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22289722&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2595&rangeEnd=2667",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2313294071541d3a2315836?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2595&rangeEnd=2667"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22289722_6_21811-21826",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "21811-21826",
      "markText": "玉在匮中求善价，钗于奁内待时飞",
